### Hadith 3:15

*Narrated Al-Aswad:*

That 'Aisha said, "O Allah's Apostle! The people are returning after
performing the two Nusuks (i.e. Hajj and 'Umra) but I am returning with
one only?" He said, "Wait till you become clean from your menses and
then go to At-Tan'im, assume Ihram (and after performing 'Umra) join us
at such-and-such a place. But it (i.e. the reward if 'Umra) is according
to your expenses or the hardship (which you will undergo while
performing it)."

